TY  - JOUR
AU  - Kim, In Joon
T1  - The Analytic Valuation of American Options
PY  - 1990
Y1  - 1990/10/01
DO  - 10.1093/rfs/3.4.547
JO  - The Review of Financial Studies
JA  - Rev Financ Stud
VL  - 3
IS  - 4
SP  - 547
EP  - 572
SN  - 0893-9454
AB  - No analytic solution exists for the valuation of American options written on futures contracts and foreign currencies for which early exercise may be optimal. This article formulates the American option valuation problem in economically and mathematically meaningful ways. This enables us to derive valuation formulas for American options. The properties associated with the optimal exercise boundary are examined, and a numerical technique to implement the valuation formulas is presented.
Y2  - 3/26/2024
UR  - https://doi.org/10.1093/rfs/3.4.547
ER  - 



